resources.string: Mauruuru koe mo to arotake, me tuku mai he urupare.
Ka nui te mihi ki a koe mo to arotake!
Mena ka whakatau koe i a maatau, ka tino maioha ki a maatau ka whakapau kaha ki te whakarato wheako pai ake.
Tena koa whakamohio mai mo etahi take i pa ki a koe.
Tena koa homai etahi atu taipitopito hei awhina i a maatau ki te tautuhi me te whakatau tere ake i to take (te iti rawa kia 6 nga tohu).
Ko te reanga teitei ka taea e tatou te eke :)
Nga arotake i runga i te Google Play
Ka whakatikahia e matou tenei take i roto i te putanga a meake nei. Aroha mai mo te raruraru
Kaore i kitea te taupānga i runga i a Google Play
